msgid ""
"Ignore the failure rate until at least this many checkouts are observed."
msgstr "Ignorovať mieru zlyhaní, kým sa nezaznamená aspoň tento počet platieb."

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1108
msgid "Sales anomaly threshold"
msgstr "Prah anomálie predaja"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1108
msgid ""
"Alert only when this many orders are typical for the hour but none arrive."
msgstr ""
"Upozorniť iba vtedy, keď je pre danú hodinu typický tento počet objednávok, "
