msgid "Operational reminders"
msgstr "Operačné pripomienky"

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:223
msgid "Never email spreadsheets of personal data - use encrypted channels."
msgstr ""
"Nikdy neposielajte tabuľky s osobnými údajmi e-mailom - používajte šifrované "
"kanály."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:224
msgid "Verify the requester before acting on access or erasure requests."
msgstr "Pred vybavením žiadosti o prístup alebo vymazanie overte žiadateľa."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:225
msgid "Log every disclosure to third parties (processors, authorities)."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamenajte každé poskytnutie údajov tretím stranám (sprostredkovatelia, "
"úrady)."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:226
msgid ""
"Report every suspected data breach to the DPO/manager within 24 hours "
"internally."
msgstr ""
"Každé podozrenie na porušenie ochrany údajov nahláste zodpovednej osobe/"
"vedúcemu interne do 24 hodín."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:235
msgid "Discovery - record timestamp, discoverer, affected systems."
msgstr ""
"Zistenie - zaznamenajte časovú značku, osobu, ktorá to zistila, dotknuté "
"systémy."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:236
msgid "Containment - isolate affected accounts/systems within 1 hour."
msgstr "Ohraničenie - izolujte dotknuté účty/systémy do 1 hodiny."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:237
msgid "Internal notification - DPO and management within 24 hours."
msgstr "Interné oznámenie - zodpovednej osobe a vedeniu do 24 hodín."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:238
msgid ""
"Assessment - document data categories, subjects affected, likely impact."
msgstr ""
"Posúdenie - zdokumentujte kategórie údajov, dotknuté osoby, pravdepodobný "
"dopad."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:239
msgid ""
"UODO notification - required within 72 hours when risk to subjects is not "
"unlikely."
msgstr ""
"Oznámenie dozornému úradu - vyžadované do 72 hodín, keď riziko pre osoby nie "
"je nepravdepodobné."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:240
msgid ""
"Subject notification - required \"without undue delay\" when risk is high."
msgstr ""
"Oznámenie dotknutej osobe - vyžadované \"bez zbytočného odkladu\", keď je "
"riziko vysoké."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:241
msgid "Remediation - patch, rotate credentials, review logs."
msgstr "Náprava - inštalujte záplaty, zmeňte poverenia, skontrolujte logy."

#: src/Service/RodoTrainingDocsService.php:242
msgid "Post-mortem - document lessons learned and update training."
msgstr ""
"Analýza po incidente - zdokumentujte získané poznatky a aktualizujte "
"školenia."

